quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  54,23,Abeekika kya Thamud baalimbisa okutiisa kwa (Nabbi waabwe Swaleh)
  54,24,"Olwo nno ne bagamba nti abaffe omuntu obuntu omu mu ffe, gwetuba tugoberera (netumala tukikola) olwo nno mazima ffe tujja kuba mu bubuze na bugwi bwa ddalu"
  54,25,Mu ffe fenna ye yaweereddwa obubaka! Nedda ssi bwekiri yye mulimba alina kyalubirira
  54,26,Enkya bajja kumanya ani mulimba omwerazi
  54,27,"(Anti) mazima ffe tujja kuweereza engamiya nga kikemo gye bali, olwo nno batunuulire nkaliriza era ogumikirize (ku nneeyisa yaabwe embi)"
  54,28,"Era bategeeze nti (okuva engamiya lwezze) ddala amazzi ga kugabanyizibwa wakati waabwe nayo, nga buli luwalo lutuukirizibwa, (nyinirwo yaalina okufuna amazzi keebe ngamiya oba bantu)"
  54,29,Olwo nno baakowoola mu nnaabwe neyeesowolayo naafumita (engamiya)
  54,30,Naye ebibonerezo byange n’okutiisa byali bitya
  54,31,"(Anti) mazima twabasindikira olubwatuka lumu, olwo nno ne baba nga ebisubi ebigwa okuva ku lugo (lwo muntu agenderera okukuuma ebisolo bye)"
  54,32,"Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu, ebeere nga ebuulirira abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,33,Abantu ba Luutu baalimbisa obubaka
  54,34,"Mazima ffe twabasindikira kibuyaga owa mayinja (eyabasanyaawo bonna) okugyako abantu b’o mu maka ga Luutu, twabawonya mu ttumbi"
  54,35,"Ekyo kyengera okuva gye tuli bwe tutyo nno, bwe tusasula oyo eyeebaza"
  54,36,Mazima (Luutu) yabeekesa okukwata kwaffe wabula nebabuusabuusa okulabula (kwe)
  54,37,"Mazima baagezaako okumusendasenda abawe abagenyi be (babasiyage) olwo nno netuziba amaaso gaabwe, ne bakomba ku bibonerezo byange n'okulabula kwange"
  54,38,Era mazima ebibonerezo ebitasalako bya bazinda mu matulutulu
  54,39,Olwo nno nebakomba ku bibonerezo byange n’okulabula kwange
  54,40,Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu ebeere nga ebuuririra abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde